, J. 1 – wing; 2 – head in frontal view; 3 – the same in lateral view. 4–6 – 
<taxonomicName authority="Černý, 2011" authorityName="Černý" authorityYear="2011" box="[204,331,1548,1566]" class="Insecta" family="Agromyzidae" genus="Agromyza" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="305" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="macedonica" status="sp. nov.">
