</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[336,405,1547,1566]" pageId="6" pageNumber="305" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
, J. 4 – head in frontal view; 5 – the same in lateral view; 6 – wing. Scales = 0.5 mm (Figs. 2–5) and 1 mm (Figs. 1, 6).
