Body length 2.38–2.55 mm (
<typeStatus box="[488,583,475,499]" pageId="8" pageNumber="307">holotype</typeStatus>
2.55 mm).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="8.[151,1127,219,1044]" pageId="8" pageNumber="307">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,278,507,531]" pageId="8" pageNumber="307">Variability.</emphasis>
The 
<typeStatus box="[339,431,508,532]" pageId="8" pageNumber="307">paratype</typeStatus>
is not distinct in colour from the 
<typeStatus box="[809,906,507,531]" pageId="8" pageNumber="307">holotype</typeStatus>
. Only the following characters are different: the width of frons is 1.30 times broader than the eye and the wing is 2.25 mm long.
</paragraph>
