<typeStatus box="[983,1076,923,947]" pageId="8" pageNumber="307">holotype</typeStatus>
was found.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="8.[151,1127,219,1044]" box="[151,396,987,1011]" pageId="8" pageNumber="307">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,277,987,1011]" pageId="8" pageNumber="307">Bionomics.</emphasis>
Unknown.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
